 <item> <title>The Enduring and Evolving Role of HBCUs</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/news/speeches/enduring-and-evolving-role-hbcus</link>
 <description>It is always important to me, and I always look forward to the opportunity to address the National HBCU Conference. This year in particular we are at a challenging, pivotal moment in supporting both the enduring and the evolving role of HBCUs.

Just four days from now, Republicans on Capitol Hill are threatening to shut down the government.</description>
