 <item> <title>U.S. Education Secretary to Deliver Morgan State University Commencement Address</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/news/media-advisories/us-education-secretary-deliver-morgan-state-university-commencement-address</link>
 <description>U.S. Secretary of Education Arne Duncan will deliver the commencement address to more than 900 graduates during Morgan State University&#039;s commencement ceremonies beginning at 10 a.m. Saturday, May 18, in Hughes Memorial Stadium on campus. Duncan will highlight Morgan State&#039;s accomplishments and the ongoing role of Historically Black Colleges and Universities (HBCUs).</description>
